    <string name="pref_title_integration">Integration with other apps</string>
    <string name="pref_summary_integration">Some apps, like LibreTasks or Tasker, allow you to automate tasks when certain events happen. Red Moon sends a public notification when it turns on and off, so those apps can respond. If you don\'t use or develop one of those apps, you can ignore the next paragraph.\n\nRed Moon broadcasts a public intent with the action `com.jmstudios.redmoon.RED_MOON_TOGGLED`. The intent contains a boolean extra with the key `jmstudios.bundle.key.FILTER_IS_ON`, which indicates whether Red Moon is toggling on or off.</string>

